"by `value` degrees. While `value` can be any number, positive or negative, "
"360 degrees makes a complete rotation. The alpha channel is left alone."
msgstr ""
":tpref:`matrixcolor` で色調を `value` 度回転するのに使用される ColorMatrix で"
